{"tid":1763693,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［急］黃絲機構要大家幫幫手！！得返1個禮拜！！","createTime":"2019-11-30T14:24:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T09:12:19.000Z","uid":118821,"like":142,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":110,"replies":[{"pid":"8cd48b14df03e37b3d15d4c53a261df0bd3ef81e","tid":1763693,"uid":118821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T14:24:44.000Z","msg":"呢間<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲機構</span>自6月反送中開始<br />\n係少數肯一直公開發表立場嘅NGO<br />\n包括<span style=\"color: gold;\">促請正苦撤回暴徒指控， 成立獨立調查委員會， 譴責警暴，全面撤回逃犯條例</span> 等等<br />\n有圖有真相！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tvrcCuU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtvrcCuU.jpg&h=6f540316&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dXK5XuZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXK5XuZ.jpg&h=5f9b0b7e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vpvkMon.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvpvkMon.jpg&h=689a752b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FGNnZJp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFGNnZJp.jpg&h=be114834&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uo3OaQa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUo3OaQa.jpg&h=bedf8dc0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n佢哋<strong>原本下星期六12月7號會賣旗籌款</strong><br />\n但<span style=\"color: green;\">popo之前係多區放咗咁多有毒催淚彈</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>考慮到當日賣旗義工（當中有好多幼稚園小朋友同家長 ）嘅安全<br />\n機構寧願取消一年一度賣旗活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n改為純籌款/賣金旗</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QgvptBw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQgvptBw.jpg&h=003ca238&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>之前濕扒幫佢哋拍過宣傳片 而家都冇得出街<br />\n所以無咩宣傳令多啲人知道</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZNSOVo3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZNSOVo3.jpg&h=d52eb1f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果佢地今年籌唔夠錢<br />\n下年會因此無左個賣旗機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望各位和理非/手足可以幫幫呢間黃絲機構<br />\n支持佢哋 繼續為社會發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時幫助更多有需要嘅人！！請幫忙推po呀！<br />\n捐款link 傳送門</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkcs.org/support/online/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcs.org%2Fsupport%2Fonline%2Findex.html&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf4RM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=c64030f0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkcs.org/support/online/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"a636cc5b3f977d5d4134484988cdd754a3f4a522","tid":1763693,"uid":118821,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T14:25:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ew5g39Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Few5g39Z.jpg&h=aa924d53&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kU3FMow.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkU3FMow.jpg&h=91bfe9ca&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5WP9EJt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5WP9EJt.jpg&h=7a5b5aaa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba4def788b2146c41a19e8b050f1861fcbc09577","tid":1763693,"uid":175159,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T14:55:42.000Z","msg":"依家先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推俾更多人知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B5mgj8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%