itedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T14:24:44.000Z","msg":"呢間<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲機構</span>自6月反送中開始<br />\n係少數肯一直公開發表立場嘅NGO<br />\n包括<span style=\"color: gold;\">促請正苦撤回暴徒指控， 成立獨立調查委員會， 譴責警暴，全面撤回逃犯條例</span> 等等<br />\n有圖有真相！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tvrcCuU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtvrcCuU.jpg&h=6f540316&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dXK5XuZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXK5XuZ.jpg&h=5f9b0b7e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vpvkMon.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvpvkMon.jpg&h=689a752b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FGNnZJp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFGNnZJp.jpg&h=be114834&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uo3OaQa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUo3OaQa.jpg&h=bedf8dc0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n佢哋<strong>原本下星期六12月7號會賣旗籌款</strong><br />\n但<span style=\"color: green;\">popo之前係多區放咗咁多有毒催淚彈</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>考慮到當日賣旗義工（當中有好多幼稚園小朋友同家長 ）嘅安全<br />\n機構寧願取消一年一度賣旗活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n改為純籌款/賣金旗</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QgvptBw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQgvptBw.jpg&h=003ca238&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>之前濕扒幫佢哋拍過宣傳片 而家都冇得出街<br />\n所以無咩宣傳令多啲人知道</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZNSOVo3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZNSOVo3.jpg&h=d52eb1f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果佢地今年籌唔夠錢<br />\n下年會因此無左個賣旗機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h